metadata.name: HIDDEN 9 - INVASION
metadata.description: Past experiences invade our minds and become who we are and how we conduct ourselves. These experiences can even find their way into our dreams, so try to make the best of your situation and dream big. I believe that our dreams are a direct representation of experiences in our lives and shape our personality…so to all of you weridos, if you ever had a dream that you were abducted by aliens… you probably were. Find the hidden “9” and 9 items.
